This repository contains code for the Jittor ModelNet40 point-cloud
classification warm-up challenge.

Third-party references:
- Jittor deep learning framework: https://github.com/Jittor/jittor
- PCT-style point-cloud transformer architecture: based on the public paper
  "PCT: Point Cloud Transformer" and common open-source PCT/DGCNN practices.
- ModelNet40 dataset: provided by the competition as preprocessed point-cloud
  files. Dataset files are not redistributed in this repository.
